Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:12.66,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Yay! We're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.33,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yuck. Minoshima's my homeroom teacher? This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:24.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,3-D...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.68,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Good morning, Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kimura-san. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.47,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Looks like we're in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:35.64,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,So you're in class D...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:39.06,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Do you see anyone we were with last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.69,Default,Nog,0,0,0,,No one among the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:42.73,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:45.61,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll make new friends soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:47.32,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,You're cute, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I-I don't think that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:55.96,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Don't be so shy and go talk to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:58.37,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,I'm in class A, so see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:00:59.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:10.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.48,Note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Welcome New Students
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:59.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why is this the first thing we do as juniors?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's because we screwed up escaping from class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.54,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can't take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.96,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm the one who can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.84,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why the heck do I have to keep my eyes on you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You should have just let us go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We're here because you turned us-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.48,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's called undue resentment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:34.52,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you don't know the term, want me to crack open your skull and hammer it into your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Your eyes are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:40.91,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,This is why I didn't want to accept being the class representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then let's finish this and go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,None of us want to waste time doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okazaki Tomoya. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's yours? {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.00,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I don't have a name to give delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:58.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I said my name, so you tell yours, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:01.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Never. I don't want to acquaint myself with idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have a wonderful personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.72,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, looks like you have an eye for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.93,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Do you at least want permission to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.48,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,There you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.41,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,H-Hey, keep off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I saved you, and you're giving me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not all right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.29,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Extra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.29,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}What Happened a Year Before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.67,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's iffy whether you deserve a word of gratitude or not, but I'll give you my thanks this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.67,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You'd better be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.55,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm Fujibayashi Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:46.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'll be with you guys for a year,\Nbut don't give me too much trouble, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There was another Fujibayashi in the next class over, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's my twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.61,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's confusing, so just call me Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:56.77,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We got to know a strange girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet she's thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's hang out by the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We've got nothing else to do, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.92,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.92,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,How's the new class?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I couldn't talk with anyone, so I was a little lonely. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Why don't you just dive in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Go introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Hello? Yeah, it's me. Me."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Ah? I'm Nagisa, your granddaughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.77,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"I got in an accident, and I'm in a little trouble..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.15,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Do at least something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:43.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm saying you need a determination on that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Be proactive! Proactive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:50.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even as a junior, it took me a lot of time to become friends with my classmates. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It looks like it'll take time this time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All it takes is a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:59.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Everyone around you wants to make friends fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:02.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Chance it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All right. I'll teach you a special trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:10.89,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You know how embarrassing it is to call your teacher "mother" by mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:15.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You adapt that and call the teacher, "Mother of Ultra"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then a rumor starts to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Could Furukawa-san be related to the Ultramen?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.65,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"I wonder if she can transform."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.11,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Let's ask her."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.66,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Hey, Furukawa-san, do you want to eat lunch together?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:31.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think that's too difficult to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then how about sharing this with the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mom's bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.96,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,There must be someone willing to suffer through eating this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.30,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Talk to kind people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Though, I think that's {\i1}too{\i0} much to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.64,San,San,0,0,0,,So my bread was... my bread was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:54.22,San,San,0,0,0,,...too much to ask for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,...love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.07,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I'll now explain tomorrow's entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.41,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,First, the juniors and seniors will sit in the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.41,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,then the freshmen will enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:16.00,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,After the ceremony, freshmen have orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.29,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Juniors and seniors will start their classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.42,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,The freshmen will-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mother of Ultra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.42,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san, you're related to the Ultramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.13,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.26,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Can you show us your transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:34.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Oh, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sorry for being so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:43.52,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't scare them by recruiting for clubs too aggressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:49.65,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Also, refrain from doing welcome events other than those organized by the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.79,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Wake up, Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.04,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Fifth period's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.68,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I guess he belongs to the cool-looking side,\Nnow that I take a close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I wonder if he has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.90,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Su-Sunohara. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What were {\i1}you{\i0} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Were you trying to kill him while he's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:34.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Or, were you trying to screw around with him in the guy-girl relationship sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.33,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Weren't you thinking something like, "Hey, he's pretty good looking"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,He looks like a total retard, but he's pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.55,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A punch erases memory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.96,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Where is this coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shut up! What's with the commotion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:54.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You were in danger, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You were about to be in a guy-girl rela-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.19,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Erasing memory, accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.69,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.20,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.28,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.04,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,I got to know her in my new class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.46,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,We're going to go check out some clothes; do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.96,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san's a really funny person, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.34,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But it's not good to linger on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.31,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,No one cares about that kind of stuff nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.39,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Here, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.23,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,It looks cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.98,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,She's right. You look nice, Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If a teacher finds us, we'll get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.33,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Next, try this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:08.00,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Oh no, Furukawa-san! A teacher's on patrol here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:11.21,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,We're going to make our run, so good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please wait! Please don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:18.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I... Even if you wish me luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:24.85,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.52,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,We're sorry about that.\NYou were so funny, we couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's fine. Though it scared me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.15,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,Such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:40.49,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,You're such a fun person, yet nobody realizes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.58,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,It'll be nice if you can make friends in your class soon. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.04,Default,Kim,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.54,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Good bye, Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:56.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Like that, I was with Kimura-san\Non the way home, so it was fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But you're alone in the class like always. {ep 22 with little change}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:06.06,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Thirty people packed in a small class, so there ought to be at least one person you can get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:13.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Even among those you pass in the hallway may be a friend forever or your soulmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But without action, they're forever no one to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How should I take action?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This comes into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Bread made by Sanae is mixed in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:29.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Give this to the class and enjoy the surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Same as those pranks you see at parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:35.05,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's bound to start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:38.05,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Furukawa-san, you come up with the funniest ideas."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"I want to be friends with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.72,San,San,0,0,0,,So my bread was... my bread was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:49.77,San,San,0,0,0,,...something meant to be enjoyed as a surprise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.65,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,...love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.70,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Six of Spades and Eight of Hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,And, Nine of Spades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:06.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,"6" and "9" come together and make the shape of "8", so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:11.42,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Your fortune-telling method's completely original as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.63,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you'll be asked out by someone tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.17,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Asked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.42,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The person will say, "I like you".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.38,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,From some nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:28.89,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I think we need to let her know how terrifying we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What? Going to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We're taking a much smarter path!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"Dear Fujibayashi Kyou-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"I fell in love with you the other day\Nand want to confess my love for you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"so please come to the reference room in the old building during lunch."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"See you there."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.54,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We're going to put that in her shoe locker tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:53.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When her heart's pounding and all,\Nwe'll watch her and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is my first time seeing a love letter with "I'm stupid" written all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.34,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,With this, Fujibayashi Kyou will be shocked and won't be able to stand tall again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:04.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We'll be able to enjoy the rest of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:08.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,True, a terror will be waiting. In many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.47,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can't wait for tomorrow to come.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.15,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,700)}Sign: Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.23,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)}Sign: Welcome New Students
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.28,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm the person on duty, so I'm going to head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.90,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.83,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,"Dear Fujibayashi Kyou-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.88,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,No way! Ryou's fortune-telling's right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Look at her blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She can be pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think we're doing something really sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.43,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Look, look, that boy's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.15,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What? You're setting targets now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:58.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I wonder how many we'll get into our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:02.03,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah. It'd be nice if we could get at least two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:03.61,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Look, he's well-built.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.41,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, that boy with the round face. Doesn't he resemble that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.41,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You know, that thing that was popular a few years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.91,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,The mascot character.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.08,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What was it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.04,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.13,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Ah, what was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.84,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I can't remember it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:25.67,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It was pretty popular, wasn't it?\NWith lots of dolls and such getting sold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.93,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,All right, we're going to the gym now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.90,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}Sign: Hikarizaka Private School Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:47.07,Default,HM,0,0,0,,New students, I hope you will have three wonderful years here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.37,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Next, salutation from the new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, am I actually looking forward to meeting the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:31.78,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,"There has been a little mishap. Please come to the rooftop."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry. Please come to the gym storage room after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What is this guy thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:54.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'd better quit it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:58.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why? You can't find something this funny that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mother of Ultra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mother of Ultra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Wow. She still doesn't realize she's being messed with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's quit it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This is only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Got to get ahead of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You better make this {\i1}it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:35.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,There has been another mishap, so this time-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.06,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Where should I make her go this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.73,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,How about, "I'll be waiting for you in Hell"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, nice idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I like that scary sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.77,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I thought I was really getting sent to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:01.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, why are we doing something like this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.34,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We're going to trick the freshmen to unwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Taking it out on others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What should I write?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:16.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,"Sunohara, Okazaki, the friendly team. By Howdy." {leave it messy}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:21.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We'll use difficult kanji to write howdy like punks do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There were several things I could point out, but nonetheless, won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:28.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then, "Youhei-Tomoya, the best. By Howdy."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you know, "by" goes before the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:40.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In that case, "Sunohara-Okazaki, the friendly Euro extreme ironing team, featuring the Hikarizaka Bros. By Howdy."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's sounds stuffy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.87,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then you write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When this breaks, that falls out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:53.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're going to drill into them that high school life's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then this is the best bit of advice I can give them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.81,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(920,400)}Sign: Welcome New Students
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.56,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's too suspicious, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.35,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Why don't you pull it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.40,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,No way. I don't want to get soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,No one's falling for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Only a moron falls for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:21.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Damn it. You mean they're smarter than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Heck, you're the lowest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:25.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is she a freshman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The collar's blue, so she must be a senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.85,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh no. She's knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.89,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Health center! Take her to the health center!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.24,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. But my head still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:47.70,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It was someone's prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.79,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I was right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.21,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It was like a scene from the Drifters, and I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.21,Note,,0,0,0,,Note: The Drifters is an old comedy group who used the falling metal tub routine often
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:53.79,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:00.55,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I've wanted to have a chat with you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:04.81,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I heard from Kimura-san that you're a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:06.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,From Kimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.94,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I finally have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.06,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Could you be my friend if that's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes! But I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Me, too. Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.45,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Could being a kindergarten teacher be as tiring as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.72,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:46.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,There's a pain in my class that causes nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Every day is a workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.31,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,But you don't look like you mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.81,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess I don't mind it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.44,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, haven't your breasts grown again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you doing this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.08,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Love Letter Mission 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:16.96,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This time, I'm pretending to be a freshman falling in love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We have so much time to waste, don't we?
